17
00:01:51,900 --> 00:01:53,100
Of course, I have to come early.

18
00:01:53,100 --> 00:01:56,600
A'Rui would be really happy

19
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:58,400
if she got to see this, too.

20
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,600
Maybe one day,

21
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:02,600
you'll find the right man, too.

22
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:07,000
Then, you'll understand why I'm doing this.

23
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:09,400
I understand.

